{"tid":50752,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"京都旅行一問","createTime":"2016-12-22T16:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T15:59:41.000Z","uid":37675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8b2e8d0dbdd565ebcd8ca05008d8257538f8da","tid":50752,"uid":37675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"京都去過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,但今次係中途站同carry朋友去<br />\n<br />\n京都係旅行中間幾日先到<br />\n<br />\n酒店就係京都站<br />\n<br />\n但我諗係夜晚5,6點先到京都,夜晚會去稻河,因為見佢24小時開<br />\n<br />\n想問有咩地方可以食晚餐??? 京都站去河原町近唔近<br />\n<br />\n由於第2日夜晚就返大阪<br />\n<br />\n有冇可能一早去到清水寺,因為有fd冇去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去食個豆腐早午餐<br />\n<br />\n10點就去嵐山,去到3,4點就返大阪,好似好趕"},{"pid":"39e487861d904273f009cc63b548f271b18a844c","tid":50752,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:27:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1137d11af18b7feaad942ace3de50ab64e17023e","tid":50752,"uid":37675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:31:39.000Z","msg":"訓先,聽日返公司回"},{"pid":"115ecdd2e4197a2a260c889a71bfd4743b9ea4e8","tid":50752,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:34:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc57b4cda523e148dda3fde2b3275f5943332b96","tid":50752,"uid":14135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:38:51.000Z","msg":"夜晚稻荷冇野睇 <br />\n建議去河源町 行街<br />\n搵一日稻荷+宇治"},{"pid":"3c26418d575c6185fe3cb9edae2dc2d2bec77c40","tid":50752,"uid":37675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:41:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夜晚稻荷冇野睇 <br />\n建議去河源町 行街<br />\n搵一日稻荷+宇治</blockquote><br />\n我地預得1.5日係京都<br />\n<br />\n稻荷去影下only"},{"pid":"27fbd33e43b25cb13405c3d663b6ae2784f91c1b","tid":50752,"uid":31629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco