"uid":6520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:37:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第一晚去河原町<br />\n第2日一早去左稻荷再去清水寺/嵐山2揀一<br />\n夜晚去稻荷做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n清水 嵐山一定要2揀1???</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果京都站係中間<br />\n<br />\n清水係東北偏東<br />\n嵐山係西北偏北<br />\n我覺得一日搞得掂<br />\n但係要好早起身，七點半左右係嵐山差唔多"},{"pid":"818d34f8b099793cea8f5aac15e9cf40052ba170","tid":50752,"uid":6520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:41:23.000Z","msg":"京都站去嵯峨南山約半個鐘<br />\n京都站坐洛巴士100號去清水約半個鐘<br />\n<br />\n自己計來回時間要幾耐<br />\n<br />\n三四點返大阪 好難囉<br />\n自己一個人行都未必得"},{"pid":"11509308a6ef3f3dbd49046a41c93bede0dcab8a","tid":50752,"uid":6520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:41:36.000Z","msg":"京都站去嵯峨南山約半個鐘<br />\n京都站坐洛巴士100號去清水約半個鐘<br />\n<br />\n自己計來回時間要幾耐<br />\n<br />\n三四點返大阪 好難囉<br />\n自己一個人行都未必得"},{"pid":"8a2e0a6eef4579fa4ba32f4aedee813a351e9745","tid":50752,"uid":6520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:41:53.000Z","msg":"屌 回左兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c635402aa35a7a751c8157888e94927603688e","tid":50752,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第一晚去河原町<br />\n第2日一早去左稻荷再去清水寺/嵐山2揀一<br />\n夜晚去稻荷做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://static1.squarespace.com/static/5500ffc7e4b0f57d71dc6073/t/562cdbd5e4b093bf1bd9233e/1445780444624/?format=750w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic1.squarespace.com%2Fstatic%2F5500ffc7e4b0f57d71dc6073%2Ft%2F562cdbd5e4b093bf1bd9233e%2F1445780444624%2F%3Fformat%3D750w&h=b9412725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜景好正架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依個景上京都塔睇好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nx2</blockquote><br />\nx3</blockquote><br />\n如果唔想去塔，你不如坐的士上將軍塚睇啦"},{"pid":"191348df9cff41ef932f95d1be75d569fcfd4b85","tid":50752,"uid":31629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:11:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第一晚去河原町<br />\n第2日一早去左稻荷再去清水寺/嵐山2揀一<br />\n夜晚去稻荷做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n清水 嵐山一定要2揀1???</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要去晒唔係唔得<br />\n你可以一早7點出發去稻荷上半山9點就走<br />\n之後唔好晒時間搭巴士去清水寺先直接搭JR上嵐山<br />\n上到嵐山睇你點行<br />\n基本上都係渡月橋天龍寺竹林 食埋晏快既大概用4個鐘左右<br />\n2點半前搭JR落京都站轉巴士去清水寺<br />\n3點半-4點可以去到清水寺<br />\n係趕D都唔係去唔晒"},{"pid":"ed3679ff20b452390acf2eb3efb21964163fc894","tid":50752,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:14:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第一晚去河原町<br />\n第2日一早去左稻荷再去清水寺/嵐山2揀一<br />\n夜晚去稻荷做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n清水 嵐山一定要2揀1???</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要去晒唔係唔得<br />\n你可以一早7點出發去稻荷上半山9點就走<br />\n之後唔好晒時間搭巴士去清水寺先直接搭JR上嵐山<br />\n上到嵐山睇你點行<br />\n基本上都係渡月橋天龍寺竹林 食埋晏快既大概用4個鐘左右<br />\n2點半前搭JR落京都站轉巴士去清水寺<br />\n3點半-4點可以去到清水寺<br />\n係趕D都唔係去唔晒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n痴線，咁趕腳都斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去東邊就唔好浪費時間行去西邊啦，唔去嵐山得唔得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674ba4b72b55ee164cfa3e9ffc2aa9e1f8b2cf4f","tid":50752,"uid":37675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:25:54.000Z","msg":"清水寺幾點仲可以去"},{"pid":"55fd3c2fa9aa56d7957fc0b620fcaaffea7c1361","tid":50752,"uid":31629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:39:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n痴線，咁趕腳都斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去東邊就唔好浪費時間行去西邊啦，唔去嵐山得唔得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢唔想2揀1想去晒就要咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>清水寺幾點仲可以去</blockquote><br />\n大部份日子6點OFF"},{"pid":"93932f1e5e654ebb41743f9ff17951b1948e0480","tid":50752,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:40:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清水寺幾點仲可以去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十一月果時開埋夜晚<br />\n勁多人<br />\n唔知而家仲有無"},{"pid":"042fc26c8a144ada5acb21171f2ca6acee131345","tid":50752,"uid":37675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T14:36:27.000Z","msg":"稻荷可能唔去<br />\n<br />\n但早D去清水寺,下午去嵐山希望6,7點返到大阪"},{"pid":"3d43b2a4eb220e60de0d9bed55396293447fcba3","tid":50752,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:57:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>清水寺幾點仲可以去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十一月果時開埋夜晚<br />\n勁多人<br />\n唔知而家仲有無</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夜間參拜都過哂。"},{"pid":"54ca096401e11c92407f705e495b45ebb21510bb","tid":50752,"uid":37675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:59:41.000Z","msg":"河原町  鴨川上面D餐廳係咪好多好早收"}]}